{"tid":1739952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有兩個傻仔跌左電話","createTime":"2019-11-19T19:48:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T01:06:59.000Z","uid":322282,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a35d273bb557bab334f9f62c3e5db5a4b53c8e69","tid":1739952,"uid":322282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T19:48:59.000Z","msg":"代po<br />\n<br />\n嗰兩個就係poly嘅手足，兩部執嘅日期都唔同<br />\n左面係粉紅色iphone<br />\n右邊係samsung唔知乜7<br />\n兩個型號都唔清楚<br />\n兩部手機都壞左開唔到或者冇反應，基本上用唔到架啦<br />\n但係基於安全考慮<br />\n有人會將兩部機銷毀<br />\n但係銷毀之前想話比機主同佢屋企人聽<br />\n佢部手機比人銷毀左，唔係落入喺狗身上<br />\n所以唔洗擔心<br />\n其實都有諗過揾番機主，但係好大機會比狗咬左<br />\n而且部機已經殘廢左用唔撚到，加上擔心有狗冒認<br />\n所以喺度通知一聲<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M0UgnDW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM0UgnDW.jpg&h=6a00eced&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ocgFPi3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FocgFPi3.jpg&h=1c6f8a95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XjJT9i8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXjJT9i8.jpg&h=557dfaf9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89fdd3ac2df61b2fc23ccfe65f3256026f3fd5c2","tid":1739952,"uid":37350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T19:49:30.000Z","msg":"個moon<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e859d8bfaedaf85382cbc95cd4588f280a144510","tid":1739952,"uid":200672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T19:50:08.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"106d5ff28d2cac61a4d0a28c335f5c34fab79acc","tid":1739952,"uid":47309,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a35d273bb557bab334f9f62c3e5db5a4b53c8e69","tid":1739952,"uid":322282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T19:48:59.000Z","msg":"代po<br />\n<br />\n嗰兩個就係poly嘅手足，兩部執嘅日期都唔同<br />\n左面係粉紅色iphone<br />\n右邊係samsung唔知乜7<br />\n兩個型號都唔清楚<br />\n兩部手機都壞左開唔到或者冇反應，基本上用唔到架啦<br />\n但係基於安全考慮<br />\n有人會將兩部機銷毀<br />\